Subject: [PATCH -mm v5 13/13] mincore: apply page table walker on do_mincore()
Date: Fri, 11 Jul 2014 14:35:49 -0400
Message-Id: <1405103749-23506-14-git-send-email-n-horiguchi@ah.jp.nec.com>
